operator.name: Preprocessing
Define Target
operator.description: Define the target column for the predictive model.

operator.name: Binning
operator.description: Discretize by binning (same range per bin).

operator.name: Frequency
operator.description: Discretize by frequency (same count per bin).

operator.name: Map Values
operator.description: Map some nominal target values to new values.

operator.name: Nominal to Binominal
operator.description: Make sure that target is binary for positive class mapping.

operator.name: Define Positive Class
operator.description: Potentially define which one should be the positive class.

operator.name: Nominal to Text
operator.description: Transform all nominal columns to text so that we make sure that all will have polynominal type after the next transformation.

operator.name: Text to Nominal
operator.description: Transform all text columns into polynominal columns.

operator.name: Numerical to Real
operator.description: Turn all numerical columns (not integers though) into real columns.
All general preprocessing steps happen inside this operator - double click on it to see the details.

operator.name: Generate Dummy
operator.description: Add a dummy nominal attribute to make sure that the loop will always deliver a result.

operator.name: Calculate No of Missings
operator.description: Calculate the number of missing values for this nominal attribute.

operator.name: Branch
Replace Nominal Missings
operator.description: Replace nominal missings with the word 'missing'.
Only replace missings if there are actually any missings.

operator.name: Replace Pos Infinite Values
operator.description: Replace positive infinity values by missing.

operator.name: Replace Neg Infinite Values
operator.description: Replace negative infinity values by missing.

operator.name: Replace Numerical Missings
operator.description: Replace numerical missings with the average of the column.

operator.name: Filter Examples
operator.description: Model on cases with label value, apply the model on cases with a missing for the target column.

operator.name: Sample (Stratified)
operator.description: Sample down to 250,000 examples in case there are more.

operator.name: Explain Predictions
operator.description: Create predictions for cases without value and add explanations for predictions.

process.description:
Results:
1. Model simulator
2. Performance from validation set (split off before modeling)
3. Model
4. Predicted data with explanation viz (only if the data had missing labels)
5. Predicted data with explanation table (only if the data had missing labels)
